23. Re1 Qd6 $44) 19... Bxd5 20. exd5 Nxd5 $6 {Black forces matters and goes
for an ending with equal material, underestimating White's dangerous passed
pawn. It would have been better to keep the tension going with 20...Nb4.} (
20... Nb4 $5 21. Nxb4 Qxb4 22. Qd2 Qc5 23. Kb1 Ne4 24. Qe1 Qd4 25. Be2 b5 $132)
21. cxd5 Nb4 22. Bc4 Nxc2 23. Kxc2 Qg6+ 24. Kc3 $5 (24. Kb3 b5 25. Bf1 Qc2+ 26.
